<#import "../parts/common.ftl" as c>

<@c.page>
    <div class="ml-5 mt-5 mb-5">
        <h4>Credit rules:</h4>
        <p>
            1) After taking the credit you will immediately receive credit sum to your card.
        </p>
        <p>
            2) You need to repay 20% more than sum that you have received earlier.
        </p>
        <p>
            3) After 1 month and during next 12 months you will automatically repay 1/12 of the sum you have to repay.
        </p>
        <p>
            4) If you do not have enough money on your balance to repay month payment, this sum will still be paid and
            your balance will be negative.
        </p>
        <p>
            5) If your balance is negative - you cannot do anything, except depositing at ATM and receiving payments.
            After your balance is negative -<br>
            you have 1 day to make it positive or you will pay penalty 1 USD every day your balance is negative.
        </p>
        <p>
            6) If you want to repay credit earlier - you can do it if you have whole sum that you should repay totally.
        </p>
    </div>
</@c.page>